// `module species.species-of-types` (done) 
#embed("008N")[]

Compare the definition to Joyal's definition of a _species_.
#embed("0081")[Species (Joyal)]

Notice that this definition requires a species to be functorial. Conveniently
for any species of types we can get functoriality in the following sense.
